HtmlItemData.Html:
The way staff view communication within a company is very important.  Please take the time to complete this survey and select the answer that most closely reflects your views.
This survey is completely confidential.

ItemTexts_Select1Data.TextValue: I believe that this company is good at communicating with its staff.
Which of the following keeps you informed the most as to what happens in this company?
We have some optional personal questions, would you like to answer them?
(These questions will help us to understand how opinions differ between different groups. Your answers will not be combined in such a way as to risk identifying individual respondents).
How long have you worked at this company?

ItemTexts_MatrixItemData.TextValue: To what extent do you agree or disagree with the following statements?
(please select one answer for each statement)

MatrixCategoryTexts.TextValue: I have attended a team meeting within the last 4 weeks.
I have a good understanding of the future direction of the company
I feel well informed about what is happening within the company
Communication between my team and other parts of the company are good
Communication within my team is good

ItemTexts_SingleLineTextItemData.TextValue: What one thing could we as a company do to improve comunication?

ItemTexts_MessageItemData.TextValue: Thank you for taking the time to complete this survey.
